# Enforce Unix-style line endings (LF) for all text files in the repository.
# This prevents issues with CRLF/LF differences across operating systems.
*.js text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf

# Denote all files that are truly binary and should not be modified.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
# Explicitly treat minified JS as binary to avoid reformatting
*.min.js binary